python-svglib (A pure-Python library for reading and converting SVG)

Svglib is a Python library for reading SVG files and converting them
(to a reasonable degree) to other formats using the ReportLab Open
Source toolkit.

HOME: https://github.com/deeplook/svglib

======================================================================
REQUIRES: python-cssselect2 python-reportlab python-tinycss2 

